File: infra/compose.yml
Role: Local Infrastructure Manifest
Purpose: Defines the multi-container orchestration environment for local development and testing, including PostgreSQL database and MinIO S3 object storage infrastructure.

Required Env Vars:
POSTGRES_USER, string, static, database owner user.
POSTGRES_PASSWORD, string, static, database user password.
POSTGRES_DB, string, static, primary database name.
MINIO_ROOT_USER, string, static, S3 root admin access key.
MINIO_ROOT_PASSWORD, string, static, S3 root admin secret key.

Dependencies:
gophkeeper-db: runs postgres container on host port 5542.
gophkeeper-s3: runs minio object storage on host ports 9000 and 9001.
gophkeeper-s3-init: ephemeral utility container, depends on gophkeeper-s3, creates target bucket gophkeeper.

Networks:
gophkeepernet: custom network bridge for internal container inter-connectivity.

Volumes:
gophkeeper_s3: persistent local storage for encrypted large binary artifacts or backups.
